Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.35,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the Kuromi from this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:04.28,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I-I'm so cute, even as a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.24,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Thanks for comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:06.54,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Want a candy, hun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.77,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Now you can be part'a\Nthe ZOMBIfy the World Project too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.52,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,ZOMBIfy the World Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:15.90,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Got that right! Zombies don't gotta\Nthink about anythin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:18.15,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,The world's way happier like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.02,RiskySubs,Gureco,0,0,0,,I'm happy bein' a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.85,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,We make more zombies\Nthrough this scallion cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.60,RiskySubs,Zombies,0,0,0,,Scallion for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:27.27,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,What?! I already drank it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:29.27,RiskySubs,Collimo,0,0,0,,You should get zombified\Nreal soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I can feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:32.98,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.00,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,I suppose since you forget\Nyour troubles overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:37.40,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,it won't work on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.80,RiskySubs,Zombies,0,0,0,,It won't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:39.94,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.77,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Besides, life's no fun\Nwithout a few challenges!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:44.60,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Ugh, you sure are difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.44,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Get rid of that eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.19,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,Welp, I can't interfere,\Nbut I can cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.56,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,You have one job, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.27,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.52,RiskySubs,Collimo,0,0,0,,So spicy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:58.02,RiskySubs,Zom!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Heat! It's every zombie's weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:00:59.94,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,Kuromi, take MM!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:02.77,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,Tap it against zombie-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:03.90,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Boop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.06,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,Universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.24,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Huh?! What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.98,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,I am the Multiverse Mobile,\Nor MM for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.26,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,An equipment used by\NUniverse Patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:16.34,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,Tapping me against a key\Nopens the door between dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:18.15,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Wait, so I'm the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.10,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,It just happens to look like you!\NFunny coincidence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.06,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:24.81,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,So if I step through this door...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.85,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,You'll go back to your home world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:28.35,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,And my mission will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.98,RiskySubs,Zombies,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.35,RiskySubs,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kuromi's keyword!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:39.98,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,"A villainess!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:43.19,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I look totally cute like this!
